MP-Gaming.COM - Game-Maps.NET

- Double floors.
- Map has excellent VIS Setup so lag should be absolute minimal on bigger servers
- Ice/water-zone in center is a Buy- and Bombzone
- Hanging hosty removed due to a bug caused by a valve update (hosty fell straight down at roundstart breaking the ice)
- 24 T Spawnpoints, 24 CT Spawnpoints
- Each side has 78 Weapon Spawnpoints, 1 AWP and 1 Scout
- 5 Grenades spawn around the map.

Creator: zunnie@mp-gaming.com / zunnie@game-maps.net

Notes: I created this map like 3 years ago but for three years long i forgot to submit it to mapsites,
sometimes i didn't feel like submitting it but anyway here it is :)

Hopefully there are some people out there who are gonna like play on this map :)
